          <avActivityComment>The danger of wet and gliding avalanches will increase but remain within the current danger level.</avActivityComment>
          <snowpackStructureComment>The rain will give rise to extreme and thorough wetting of the snowpack in all aspects below approximately 2300 m. These conditions will cause a very rapid weakening of the snowpack. &lt;br/&gt;</snowpackStructureComment>
